      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) used as QoI in both validation and COU, providing direct correspondence. Minor concern that in-vitro NIH measurement protocol differs slightly from in-vivo clinical metric, but this is considered acceptable at current maturity."
    },
